%T A396954 1484292174750,42070172118975,1272835062298800,40960006475763375,
%U A396954 1397384174175239250,50389543681395793875,1915346130462454189500,76551085580677155322875,3209657724814568260983750,140882413190896544606814375
%N A396954 Number of rooted binary time-consistent leaf-labeled galled trees with n leaves and exactly 1 gall.
%H A396954 Lily Agranat-Tamir, Michael Fuchs, Bernhard Gittenberger, and Noah A. Rosenberg, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.tcs.2026.116075">Enumerative combinatorics of unlabeled and labeled time-consistent galled trees</a>, Theor. Comp. Sci. 1082 (2026), 116075. See Table 5.
%F A396954 a(n) = (n+2)*(2*n)!/(n!*2^n) - 3*2^(n-1)*n!.
%F A396954 E.g.f.: ((4 - 3*sqrt(1 - 2*x) - 6*x)/(1 - 2*x)^(3/2) - 1)/2. - _Stefano Spezia_, Jun 11 2026
%e A396954 With n=3, there is only one unlabeled time-consistent galled tree, containing a root node and a gall from which three leaves descend. If the leaves are labeled A, B, and C, then three choices are possible for the label of the leaf that is descended from the single reticulation node.
%t A396954 a[n_]:=(n+2)*(2*n)!/(n!*2^n) - 3*2^(n-1)*n!; Array[a,21] (* _Stefano Spezia_, Jun 11 2026 *)
%Y A396954 Cf. A001147(n+1) for trees with no galls, A380256(n) for unlabeled time-consistent galled trees with one gall.
%K A396954 nonn,easy
%O A396954 1,3
%A A396954 _Noah A Rosenberg_, Jun 11 2026
